description: North Texas is finally getting a taste of true authentic Italian cuisine, all thanks to Mo’s That’s Amore! After taking on a job at her favorite restaurant and learning from the best, Mo now offers her expertise and passion for food to the streets of Fort Worth. Mo’s is more than just a food truck, it’s a flavor portal into delicious Italy with every bite.  With pizza, heroes, and more, all made with the finest Italian ingredients, come try a slice with quality so divine, “and you’ll sing vita bella!”
name: Mo's That's Amore
